            "title": "Weighted Decline Sit-up Instructions",
            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Start by lying on a decline bench with your feet secured at the top and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.",
                    "Hold a weight plate or dumbbell against your chest with both hands.",
                    "Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the bench, curling your torso towards your knees.",
                    "Pause at the top of the movement and squeeze your abs.",
                    "Slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.",
                    "Repeat for the desired number of reps."
                ]
            }
